{"tid":1740384,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"建議全港文宣 - 示威者絕不在區選當日發起任何抗爭","createTime":"2019-11-20T02:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T12:31:11.000Z","uid":83375,"like":38,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"5e7a9186ea22dbe036aef7d20e3c8472e31937d1","tid":1740384,"uid":83375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:11:53.000Z","msg":"唔好屌我咩血債票償住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為我十分怕有啲<span style=\"font-size: small;\">非</span>自己友專登搞事，<br />\n然後政府<span style=\"font-size: small;\">按佢哋劇本</span>拖延，<br />\n最後入曬我哋數</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n所以，希望各文宣手足全力做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n表面講<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「示威者絕不在區選當日抗爭，搞事者必是鄉黑/藍絲/警臥底...etc」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n內在更加係要向全世界展示我哋要為香港求變嘅心：<br />\n選票數字=民意(求變嘅心)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾全世界睇我哋係公平競爭取勝，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只有港共政府先會偷偷摸摸搞做手腳</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我哋唔可以俾政府得逞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37957d96199cd7be8318c3fb8eac97a41d11337e","tid":1740384,"uid":83375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:13:07.000Z","msg":"推一次當推十次，繼續塞鐵"},{"pid":"89f6f